<h1>  </h1>

<font face="avenir">
<center> 
<p> listen: </p> 
<p> my father speaks urdu </p> 
<p> language of dancing peacocks </p> 
<p> rosewater fountains </p> 
<p> even its curses are beautiful. </p> 
<p> he speaks hindi </p> 
<p> suave and melodic </p> 
<p> earthy punjabi </p> 
<p> salty rich as saag paneer </p> 
<p> coastal kiswahili laced with arabic, </p> 
<p> he speaks gujarati </p> 
<p> solid ancestral pride. </p> 
<p> five languages </p> 
<p> five different worlds </p> 
<p> yet english </p> 
<p> shrinks </p> 
<p> him </p> 
<p> down </p> 
<p> before white men </p> 
</center>
